query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-intent',
'cakephp-3.0',
'cocoa-touch',
'dropdown',
'dynamics-crm',
'electron',
'escaping',
'grid',
'html-email',
'python-3.x',
'uitableview',
'woocommerce',
'xmlhttprequest');
